# Volunteering vocabulary

## Namespaces
### Ontology Base URI
prefix :                <https://ns.volunteeringdata.io/>

### Core W3C ontologies (OWL 2 reserved vocabulary)
prefix rdf:             <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>
prefix rdfs:            <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
prefix owl:             <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#>
prefix xsd:             <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#>

### Other namespaces used
prefix dc:              <http://purl.org/dc/terms/>
prefix geo:             <http://www.w3.org/2003/01/geo/wgs84_pos#>
prefix skos:            <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#>
prefix time:            <http://www.w3.org/2006/time#>
prefix vcard:           <http://www.w3.org/2006/vcard/ns#>
prefix vann:            <http://purl.org/vocab/vann/>


## Location Class
:Location
    a owl:Class ;
    rdfs:subClassOf geo:SpatialThing ;
    rdfs:isDefinedBy <https://ns.volunteeringdata.io/> ;
    rdfs:label "Time"@en ;
    rdfs:comment "Any location related to volunteering activities."@en ;
    dc:description "Volunteering Activity Location"@en ;
.


### Object Properties
:locationSession
    a owl:ObjectProperty ;
    rdfs:isDefinedBy <https://ns.volunteeringdata.io/> ;
    rdfs:domain :Location ;
    rdfs:range :Session ;
    rdfs:label "session has location"@en ;
.


### Datatype Properties
:locationName
    a owl:DatatypeProperty ;
    rdfs:isDefinedBy <https://ns.volunteeringdata.io/> ;
    rdfs:subPropertyOf :name ;
    rdfs:domain :Location ;
    rdfs:label "location has name"@en ;
.

:locationAddress
    a owl:DatatypeProperty ;
    rdfs:isDefinedBy <https://ns.volunteeringdata.io/> ;
    rdfs:subPropertyOf :address ;
    rdfs:domain :Location ;
    rdfs:label "location has address"@en ;
.

:locationLatitude
    a owl:DatatypeProperty ;
    rdfs:isDefinedBy <https://ns.volunteeringdata.io/> ;
    rdfs:subPropertyOf :latitude ;
    rdfs:domain :Location ;
    rdfs:label "location has latitude"@en ;
.

:locationLongitude
    a owl:DatatypeProperty ;
    rdfs:isDefinedBy <https://ns.volunteeringdata.io/> ;
    rdfs:subPropertyOf :longitude ;
    rdfs:domain :Location ;
    rdfs:label "location has longitude"@en ;
.
